EXPRESS 7.2, A UNIVERSAL VERSION OF THE COMPANYS STREAMLINED VERSION OF LOGIC

PRO 7.2 THAT PROVIDES A BASIC SET OF PROFESSIONAL TOOLS TO COMPOSE AND PRODUCE

