V. APPLE COMPUTER, INC.

PLAINTIFF MACSOLUTIONS, INC.,

A FORMER APPLE AUTHORIZED RESELLER, FILED THIS LAWSUIT AGAINST THE COMPANY ON JANUARY 20,

